+ Pivot Rows\ninto Columns
++ What is Pivoting?
+++ Long format → Wide format
++++_ Values in a column → column headers
+++ Good for cross-tabular reports
++ SQL PIVOT Clause
+++ Aggregate function required
++++_ Multiple rows → single cell
+++ FOR ... IN (values AS col_name)
++++_ Define new column names
+++ Multiple aggregations possible
++++_ SUM(...) AS total, AVG(...) AS avg
-- PySpark groupBy + pivot
---_ .groupBy("year")
---_ .pivot("quarter")
---_ .agg(sum("revenue"))
-- Use Case
---_ Quarterly revenue by region
---_ Sales by product & month
